question: Tī 2007 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t, 'Investment' kap 'other assets' ê chóng kè-chí sī siáⁿ-chōe?
Tī 'investment' kap 'other assets' chit nn̄g chióng tài-sán tiong, ūi-tio̍h 'realized and unrealized gains / ( losses ) net', to̍h-sī siáⁿ chi̍t ê tài-sán ê choa̍t-tùi bô͘-lō͘ sńg ê su-khì khah tuā?
Chik-sek-e 2008 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t, 'tāi-khòan' ê kiat-sòan choán-chè hō͘ chū-sū ê jī-bīn kap āu-sû ê kà-óng ū tīn-chiat bô? Chhí-chū lí ê suan-chek.
answer: Sī, chè-sòan sī tīn-chiat. Suan-chek sī: $1240 (khai-tiâm chè-sòan) - $409 (sêng-lī/sńg-sit) + $11 (chè-bōi/bōi-bōi) - $29 (chèng-chí thâi-chè) = $813, tòe pó-chòan ê kiat-sòan.

question: Tī 2007 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t kàu 2008 nî 12 goe̍h 31 ji̍t ê choân pō͘ kî-kan, sán-phín kè-siàu ūi ê choân-thé chha-pia̍t sī siáⁿ-mih?
Tī siánn-ê sán-phín lūi ê 'level 3 ê net chōa-ji̍p hām/ia̍h-sī chhut-khì' sêng-ûi sán-phín kè-tiâu ê tùi-sîng cheng-chi̍t?
Tī 'tōa-suán-sîng lîm-sî ê sún-sit' lāi-bīn, ū hō-chóaⁿ phiah ê lâi-chū 'tāi-khu-á'?
Tng-ji̍t ê 'chúi-chha̍k hām bô-chúi-chha̍k ê tit-e̍k / (sún-sit) net' hō͘ 'kî-tāi sêng-pún' sī $ -16, nā-sī ióng-á sī 0, án-ni December 31, 2008 ê sin chha̍p-chòe hō͘ 'kî-tāi sêng-pún' ē sī kúi-ā?

Tùi 'investments' ê su-liāu lâi koán, 'realized and unrealized gains / ( losses ) net' hām 'total net ( losses ) ... relating to assets still held at the reporting date' chit nn̄g ê koan-hē sī siâⁿ-chē?
answer: Siaⁿ chin cheng, ti̍t-chiap ê koan-hē. 'total net ( losses ) ... relating to assets still held' ($-366) chiàm liáu total 'realized and unrealized gains / ( losses ) net' ($-409) ê 89.5%. Che ì-bī tio̍h kî-kan ê đầu net losses chin chē sī unrealized hām tùi hit-ê tài-sán ê kòan-hē, in hit-ê tài-sán sui-jiân oân-choân iáu-bōe bē tiāu tī kî-kan ê tiāu-cha ji̍t. Che ì-bī tio̍h kî-kan ê đầu net losses chin chē sī unrealized hām tùi hit-ê tài-sán ê koan-hē, in hit-ê tài-sán sui-jiân oân-choân iáu-bōe bē tiāu tī kî-kan ê tiāu-cha ji̍t.
